unk_9c63f9d.value:
OWC_SMP_CHECK()
-- juice
Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(VFX_SOURCE, 10)
Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectIntensity(VFX_SOURCE, 1)
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(VFX_SOURCE, EG_HARMLESS_BURST)
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(VFX_SOURCE, SFX_DEMON_WALLA)

-- summon demons
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idSelf, "base")

if Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, 100) <= 20 then
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idSelf, "elites")
else
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idSelf, "noElites")
end

-- delay cultist activation to sell fantasy that they are summoning the demons
Hydra.Wait(1.5)

Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idSelf, sigilId) 	

for i, cultist in pairs(CULTISTS) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(cultist) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(cultist) then 
		Hydra.ActorRemoveMergedAIState(cultist, WORSHIP_AI)
	end
end

unk_993f312.value:
SPAWN_LOCS = {}
ANIM_WORSHIP = Hydra.ReferencePower("Cultist_Worship")

-- this value should match the time in usz_smp_summon_demon
ATTRACTOR_DURATION = 2

CULTIST_SIGIL_DECALS = {
	Hydra.ReferenceEffectGroup("fxKit_persistentSigilDecal_cultist_01"),
	Hydra.ReferenceEffectGroup("fxKit_persistentSigilDecal_cultist_02"),
	Hydra.ReferenceEffectGroup("fxKit_persistentSigilDecal_cultist_03"),
	Hydra.ReferenceEffectGroup("fxKit_persistentSigilDecal_cultist_04")
}

for i, cultist in pairs(CULTISTS) do 
	-- merge worship AI
	Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(cultist, WORSHIP_AI, cultist, 0)
	Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(cultist, "SMP_Monsters")
end

Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idSelf, 8)
sigilId = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSelf, CULTIST_SIGIL_DECALS[Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, #CULTIST_SIGIL_DECALS)], true)
